"{\"uid\": \"indailysa.com.au-news-archive-2024-07-24-olympic-athletes-warned-after-attacks-on-aussies-in-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australian's Olympic athletes in Paris have been advised not to travel alone or wear their uniforms in public after two violent attacks on Australians in 48 hours.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.8958124867255839, \"rank\": 0.10941359322335652, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.824802985901407e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French police are investigating allegations a 25-year-old Australian woman was gang-raped by five men during a night out near the Moulin Rouge.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.638835238122796e-39, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.8958124867255839, \"rank\": 0.10941359322335652, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0338151090041502e-29, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack came just days before\\u00a0the Olympic Games opening ceremony in Paris on Friday\\u00a0(Saturday AEST).\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.824802985901407e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 407, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harrowing CCTV has emerged of the woman entering a kebab shop in central Paris' party district to seek help after the alleged violent attack.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Closed-circuit_television\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.198293906655453e-13, \"text\": \"CCTV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Closed-circuit_television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Closed-circuit_television\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"score\": 0.9989074627656576, \"rank\": 0.0010937321775834222, \"text\": \"kebab\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kebab\"}, {\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.824802985901407e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The footage, obtained by the Seven Network, shows the woman being comforted in the store by staff and diners early on Sunday (local time).\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.865046856053494e-14, \"text\": \"Seven Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seven_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At one point a man, whom the woman claims was among her attackers, enters the takeaway shop.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is seen lingering and then approaching the alleged victim and patting her on the back before fleeing.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The kebab shop owner told Seven the woman could not stop crying and that her dress was damaged.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just 48 hours later, two members of Nine's Olympics broadcast team say they were the victims of an attempted robbery as they walked to their accommodation in the city's north-east on Monday (Paris time).\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9921336085624206e-30, \"text\": \"Nine\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.824802985901407e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nine newspapers report the attackers tried to snatch the tech employees' backpacks and they were assaulted in the scuffle that ensued.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian team's chef de mission Anna Meares said Olympians had been reminded about protecting their safety after the alleged attack on the woman.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.601094001110251e-33, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9981918381176121, \"rank\": 0.0017850621068446265, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It sounds horrific,\\\" said Meares on Tuesday (AEST).\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, our hearts go out to the woman involved, and we hope she's been cared for and supported in the trauma that she's experienced.\\\"\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meares said the security presence was high for Australia's Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6467038822761056, \"rank\": 0.5463027598967979, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What information we are passing onto our athletes is that security presence is really, really high and that's in order for them to act as quickly as possible to keep them safe,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not yet have any feedback from our athletes that they have felt unsafe.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are encouraging them, if they go out of the village, not to go out on their own, not to wear [their] team uniform, just to wear plain clothes.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are just waiting on further information on the actual case itself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French newspapers report that police are investigating the gang-rape allegation, which came just days before the Paris Olympic Games begin, with thousands of tourists in the city.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8344245477546117, \"rank\": 0.1934383986484753, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officers are trying to piece together the Australian woman's movements on Saturday night and early Sunday.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.8958124867255839, \"rank\": 0.10941359322335652, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been no arrests, but the BBC reports prosecutors are treating the investigation as gang rape.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9919103673578565, \"rank\": 0.008155590692125184, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack reportedly occurred at the Boulevard de Clichy, a famous street in the 18th arrondissement near the Moulin Rouge nightclub.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2757, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0338151090041502e-29, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Home Affairs Minister Clare O'Neil told\\u00a0Sunrise\\u00a0she felt \\\"physically sick\\\" when reading about the attack on the woman.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6467038822761056, \"rank\": 0.5463027598967979, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2794, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Office\", \"score\": 0.9999999881338227, \"rank\": 1.1866346111913804e-08, \"text\": \"Home Affairs\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Office\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Office\"}, {\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_O'Neil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare O'Neil\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_O'Neil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_O'Neil\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\", \"score\": 0.9999997608843217, \"rank\": 2.3911567892237476e-07, \"text\": \"Sunrise\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just want to say to her on behalf of the Australian Government, every Australian [is] thinking about her today,\\\" O'Neil said on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 3055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9999894560497701, \"rank\": 1.0538535153998506e-05, \"text\": \"Australian Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People are entitled to travel to a beautiful country like France and do so safely.\\\"\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3116, \"end\": 3122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9926197023016072, \"rank\": 0.006265980660034973, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Neil said the Australian Olympic team seemed to be aware of the potential security and safety issues facing athletes.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3159, \"end\": 3182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9977861827375519, \"rank\": 0.0022187291230736416, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a shame they do not feel like they can go out and wear their uniform,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want them to have a good Olympics and bring home the medals and enjoy the experience.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris is not necessarily an unsafe place.\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3445, \"end\": 3450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.824802985901407e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French are doing all they can to keep all the participants in the Olympics as well as the spectators as safe as they could be.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8344245477546117, \"rank\": 0.1934383986484753, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone should be aware.\\\"\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"-TND  On the journey from hale to frail, which physical attribute is the first to fade and rob you of independence?\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Reserve Bank of Australia board is widely tipped to keep rates on hold at its meeting today but a dovish turn in its post-meeting statement could lay the foundations for a pre-Christmas cut.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A presidential election unlike any other in US history has entered its last full day, with Donald Trump and Kamala Harris scrambling for an edge in a tight contest each portrays as an existential moment for America.\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4003, \"end\": 4005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.7496790904550866, \"rank\": 0.32762319403119416, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Armed_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 4050, \"end\": 4062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.99999959380838, \"rank\": 4.0580375657484676e-07, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4067, \"end\": 4073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.73129747887406e-12, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamala_Harris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel's Air Force says it has struck Hezbollah intelligence assets near Damascus in an attack on key infrastructure in Syria that Syrian officials say targeted civilian sites.\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4176, \"end\": 4182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israe